name: ruining things since the 50's
description: it was a dark and stormy night. it was a hot summer night. it was a cool breeze of a night. it was a cold winter night. it was a spring moonlit night. it was dark and we were surrounded by a black blanket of sky and couldn't have been closer than the parking break would allow until a small sound. a small feeling like a hint of a nail on a chalkboard and there's nothin' like a good urban legend to ruin things, er i mean keep the kids safe.
